{"word":"περιαιρέω","slug":"περιαιρέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>περιαιρέω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:περί\">περί</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:αἱρέω\">αἱρέω</a></el>] ‘take <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> away that is around or attached to <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a>’, <b>remove <a href='B:540 3:16'>2 Cor 3:16</a>; <a href='B:650 10:11'>Hb 10:11</a>; cast off/slip</b> an anchor <b><a href='B:510 27:40'>Ac 27:40</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prob.\">prob.</a> <b><a href='B:510 28:13'>28:13</a></b> is to be understood in this sense, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <el>τὰς ἀγϰύρας</el> supplied<b>.</b> By <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ext.\">ext.</a>, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> of hope at its end <b>be cut off, be abandonedvs. 20.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:περιάγω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:περιάπτω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}